      "widgets_values": [
        "Z-IMAGE TURBO - fast TEXT to IMAGE (local, free)\n\nNear-instant generation (~3-6s) with the cleanest in-image TEXT of any\nlocal model. Great for quick ideas / replacing Midjourney for fast work.\n\nKEY SETTINGS (already set):\n  - KSampler: steps 8, CFG 1.0, sampler dpmpp_sde, scheduler beta\n    (Turbo model: keep CFG=1, steps 4-10. More steps != much better.)\n  - ModelSamplingAuraFlow shift = 3\n  - CLIPLoader type MUST be 'lumina2' (Z-Image uses it), encoder qwen_3_4b\n  - Negative prompt is ignored at CFG 1 (leave empty).\n\nFor best text rendering, describe the exact words in quotes in the prompt."
      ],
